song.title: Celtic Romances
song.info: Used in BitJam Vol. 1.1 : Solaris by Bitfellas. Something completely different, a bit of a try for Robin Hood / Last of the Mohicans mood. After the first song there are also two other songs making this yeat another multi part module (1st part 00:00, 2nd 03:39, 3rd 09:29). Composed in 1996 - probably the last tune before starting again in 2005.
